item.title: CVE-2023-30532|2024-08-02T14:28:51.524Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20turboscript%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins TurboScript Plugin 1.3 and earlier allows attackers with Item/Read permission to trigger builds of jobs corresponding to the attacker-specified repository.
